Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 20
Set Width 1000
Set Height 580
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Padding 24

Type "ruby -Ilib exe/citedhealth ingredients biotin"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "ruby -Ilib exe/citedhealth evidence biotin nutritional-deficiency-hair-loss"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "ruby -Ilib exe/citedhealth papers --year 2024"
Enter
Sleep 3s
